*   `.github/workflows/ci.yml`: The `Heresy Detector Discovery` job is configured correctly under the `heresy-detector` job identifier (lines 206–231), running `scripts/check-heresies.sh --report heresy-detector-report.json` and uploading the JSON output as an artifact.

